Requirement of Attribution (BY - Attribution): For every party effectuating the utilization or adaptation of The Work, the provision of suitable attribution to Umut Emre YILMAN, in strict compliance with applicable statutory regulations, and the supply of the valid Uniform Resource Locator (URL) affording access to this license instrument, has been mandated as an indisputable statutory obligation. The explicit citation of the "Aresia" brand during the execution of said attribution is accepted as a procedural protocol strongly recommended in consideration of the Work's provenance.

Non-Commercial Restriction (NC - NonCommercial): The utilization of The Work, irrespective of the medium or modality employed, for the exclusive purpose of commercial objectives is strictly and definitively precluded. This restriction definitively and absolutely prohibits the procurement or sale of the software itself, the collection of pecuniary recompense in exchange for associated services rendered, or the application of the software as a critical constituent of any commercial product or enterprise.

